Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You have 1 new unread message.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My Hokkaido employment matter has been settled.{/I've decided about working in Hokkaido}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming once again to Tokyo \Nto vacate{/move out of} my flat{/mansion}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been the most caring up until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really better this way,{/Was this really a right thing to do,}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.03,0:02:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:31.15,Song,,0,0,0,,{\q2\fade(900,900)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad4\blur1\4c&H5A694E&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs65\pos(310,30)\3c&HD0BFA9&}Episode 22\N {\fs120}\N\N\N\N\N\NIncandescence
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Align to the Sakura bloom!{/Come, sakura combination - unsure about zoroi part}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going ahead,{/not waiting you} Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi is putting up quite a fight!{/doing his best}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Daiba is unaffected.{/pushing him aside}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what you'd expect from a King's battle. \NCan't take my eyes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is better this way.{she uses the same wording as Master in the car before, except with asking suffix}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Intermission?{\i0}{/take a break/rest}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,With {first }half of the battle behind, \Nwe are now entering an hour-long intermission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Intermission?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Some cold water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Will bring right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't waste your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're supposed to rest our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become quite formidable.{/strong}\NGreat match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{From now on, }I'm finishing the rest of it in one sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba should too \Nbe ready to carry it to the finish.{/Lit: you too, please find your resolve/preparedness}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay sharp.{/don't let your guard down}{I feel that this line is supposed to have an oblique second implication, like "I know something you don't but I don't wanna give it out with my words, yet I'm tempted to somehow indirectly let you know"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Daiba stays sharp too.{he doesn't actually say "then/too" which leaves room for doubt as to what is the object here: maybe it's "don't let your guard down towards daiba" or "I'm keeping a close eye on daiba"}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Most certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Otonashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A special supply{Lit: food/refreshments for a prisoner/worker - I don't know how else to handle it} from Mr. Shibaura \Nhas been delivered to your room{added}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,From Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll head to the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This sure will help regain my spirits!{unsure, maybe he's encouraging daiba to "cheer up"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll go get some rest \Nin my own room as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight is between me and Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you obstruct it{/get in the way} ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba collapsed on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get some rest there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirits!{/Cheer/Determination}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,10 more minutes.{he actually says ago, but I suppose you can use mae this way too}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Daiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't returned from his seclusion yet.{/Still haven't returned from elsewhere}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll just wait here a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, Daiba too \Nis completely cool and collected{about this}{/easygoing}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,3 minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return to your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.26,0:07:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to hurry{/be impatient} like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Until Daiba returns, we can't start anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check{/see} his condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is allowed into the waiting room -
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't that fine by you, Mr. Dealer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,However...{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, we will resume the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I still plan to win, Daiba.{/I won't lose}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I was hoping for.{/I couldn't ask for more}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me what you're worth,{/come boldly} Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A clean cut!{guess}{/with bare finger/in one move?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No... He aligned{/assembled} it in a blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Finger of God's worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba is amazing, just as always!{/as expected}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi is steadily falling behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he is playing to{/showing off} his true ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What a curious feeling. \NNot a hint of fear in me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, Daiba's devotion{/vigor} is rather comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go, Daiba Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hardly believe it...\NOtonashi is starting to catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an impressive momentum!{/drive}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the fight Ryo yearned for?{/desired}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just yet, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:09:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Step off!{/don't touch him}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm here for.{/I want you to let me handle this}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is malignant intracerebral tumor.{/it's because of a tumor in his brain tissue}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A life-threatening condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to keep it a secret until now.{/kept silent ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I will reiterate what I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's any danger,\Nthe match should be called off{/interrupted/cancelled}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I ask you to call the match off at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my verdict as attendee.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, \NDaiba is beyond saving.{/we won't be able to rescue ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The ER team{/ambulance} has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking Daiba {away }with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do, Daiba?{It sounds a bit like "what are you implying with that"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The match is not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense!{/Don't be unreasonable!} \NI would never concede to{/acknowlege} such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to walk me{/accompany me} back to my machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Daiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In that condition...{/with such body}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The car is ready.{/preparations are over} \NWe can now transport the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please proceed.{/do it} \NI have already arranged it with{/contacted} the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Daiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please step away from him.{/don't touch...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can lend you my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We are resuming the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about your promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You should keep burning in Slothium{/stand fast in ...},{rather, it's "keep combusting your life" idiom I used earlier, but that seems too heavy on the cps here} \NOtonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should keep fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.74,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He can no longer be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than die in hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,he would die here!{the original line is rather less pivoting, something like "either he dies ... or ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry to have kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The match will now be resumed \Nbetween King Daiba Ryo and General Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Start pressing{/hitting}, Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold back.{/That's better.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't press.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All that pachislot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,what purpose does it serve{Lit: "what is that machine/instrument" but they usually use "dai" for machines, so it has to be something else, though I can only wander what exactly}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It never made a single person happier!{/didn't ever brought happiness to a single person}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{[I've had ]}Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can press no more buttons, Daiba.{/I'm not hitting already}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You must go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{[Just] }Not you...{/you alone}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what I chose myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because it's the right thing to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but rather because you can only choose one.{/It's not about being the correct choice, but rather about [one always] having to only choose one [of two options]}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, \NI didn't choose pachislot.{eg: I didn't pick to play pachislot over saving my life}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it was you who chose it.{/your choice}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"Daiba dies either way?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare to call yourself a doctor after that?!{/What kind of ... are you}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done with the Slothium.{/'ve had enough of ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not playing{/pressing a single button in} pachislot ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's your wish.{/I heard you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, \NRyo told me this:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I myself only live in the present moment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's our perception \Nthat constitutes{/defines} the present.{\i0}{/the present is made of our memories}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}By piling up perception after perception, \Nwe build up our own present moment.{\i0}{/Lit: moment after a moment, we accumulate perceptions to make our present of them}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, from it, a future is born.{\i0}{/the future can only come from that}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, it's this way, too.{/This is true for me as well.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after Ryo dies, \NI will remain faithful to this conviction.{/Not even Ryo's death will change a thing for me}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,really have no regrets, doing this{added}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi's retirement means Daiba's win.{really noisy, maybe "if otonashi doesn't return, daiba will win"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. Otonashi has higher score, \Nso he'll be declared winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what will become of the match now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just put it frankly already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer have to keep going, Daiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it all the way to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Fushina,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,have I managed to get close enough to you?{I'm unsure he's addressing fushina, maybe he was getting close to something else}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my business{/issue} only.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Man must decide by himself \Non a place to die.{/where to die}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba is recuperating already!{/catching up/making a comeback}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is{/what about} Otonashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point anymore, Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over with Slothium!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You will remain the Ultimate King for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The match is not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I will overthrow Daiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's roll, Daiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Step down, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This fight is between me and Daiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no one can get in our way{/obstruct it}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,For future's sake, I'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me.{/that's better}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Ryo was right when he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.20,0:20:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he is to become much stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,On my part, I just envy those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the beginning of match, \N8 hours have elapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Update on the current scores: \NUltimate King Daiba Ryo - 22 785 coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)}Challenger Otonashi Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We clash.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We overlap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.84,0:22:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We make history.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.45,0:22:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,While time is breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere{added} inside it, \Nmemories{in the next ep I'll make this "history" but here I don't care} are engraved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:50.16,Song,,0,0,0,,Final episode: \NTime
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your way of life \Nis that of a shooting star.
